In order to make this project work, you need to:
- put directories graphics, levels and sounds, and icon.bmp (which are located
  in resources) in directory where your executable file is located
- (on Windows) put dlls from libs/bin in directory where your executable file
  is located

*.tlp files are just 7z archives and you can modify them using any software
that supports 7z format.

Compiling/running on linux:
Needed libs:
- libSDL-1.2.14
- libSDL_image-1.2.10
- libSDL_mixer-1.2.8
- libGLEW-1.5
